ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:48:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/103359_f4d8ed2bda8fc123b3a2bacdebb7c484.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F103359_f4d8ed2bda8fc123b3a2bacdebb7c484.jpg&h=d703f29f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樓豬可以一戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗我會嬲但唔會嬲到喊囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者你咁諗 有一件你好鐘意做既事 你都想你另一半有興趣可以多個話題 點知佢做做下瞓左 咁你都好無癮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咁啩 女人心海底針你唔係唔知下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實女人係咪唔會諗下啲正經野<br />\n例如第日要考試所以唔好咁夜訓呢啲？</blockquote><br />\n成日都話 溫唔切書<br />\n但又晒時間睇呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c944c3625a1f8522ab407648cbe33ef79e99bc","tid":247523,"uid":95515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:49:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係缺乏安全感嘅表現<br />\n佢覺得你唔鍾意佢嘅興趣，<br />\n彼此之間有距離，<br />\n所以覺得好驚，<br />\n驚你會鍾意其他同你有共同興趣嘅女仔，<br />\n於是用嬲嚟掩飾自己嘅恐懼</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c062ad846d3ed2b547b79c7465ff85a89923bb2","tid":247523,"uid":95515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:50:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真，應該嬲你冇掂佢。<br />\n<br />\n你地係咪好耐冇見？</blockquote><br />\n日日都一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e682426dcf337b7df424a0de5b321215c4b69b47","tid":247523,"uid":95515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:54:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一  肥婆性格扭曲係基本<br />\n第二  女人戇鳩係常識<br />\n<br />\n睇到上面有女留言話攰咪主動講唔想睇,下次先<br />\n真係好撚表現到女性果種鳩<br />\n你作為女性真係認為對女性黎講,男性係有拒絕而無後果嘅可能性?<br />\n男話唔睇-&gt;女話無事(